{"tid":1042208,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"曼城6.5億鎊轉會Puma10年","createTime":"2019-03-01T11:44:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-01T12:12:04.000Z","uid":93891,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"2dea58548d593ef4ca1388cfe7560220baf901a0","tid":1042208,"uid":93891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-01T11:44:47.000Z","msg":"英超勁旅曼城今日宣布來季將會「轉會」，球衣贊助商由Nike改成Puma。據報新合約價值6.5億鎊，是繼曼聯之後英超史上最貴的球衣合約。<br />\n曼城靠阿古路12碼險勝韋斯咸<br />\nPuma與City Football Group的合作關係將於今年夏天開始，合約將為期10年，代表「藍月亮」下季起將穿起該德國運動名牌所設計的戰衣出賽。對於雙方合作，曼城行政總裁形容為史無前例：「今日是歷史性的一天，因為我們所決定的合作簡直是史無前例，這包括了4大洲及5間球會。」Puma的合作不限於曼城，還包括了City Football Group其下多間球會如墨爾本城及基羅納等。<br />\n<br />\nCity Football Group與Puma是次合約價值高達6.5億鎊，是英超史上繼曼聯與Adidas的合約之後金額最高的一份球衣贊助。（<a href=\"http://Goal.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FGoal.com&d=u7xsq8u58TeopDPyjGw7C5HrfcRVF4fwerrMnmH2A0w%3D&h=9227bee8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">Goal.com</a>）<br />\n<br />\n可以重課 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65c3c9dc23d8c5331af9ad17079d3983963b8b46","tid":1042208,"uid":53498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-01T11:56:43.000Z","msg":"唔撚貴合約,要一個月轉一次款"},{"pid":"736b97371bbe1ea58412b32885c7db097fb546d9","tid":1042208,"uid":65298,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-01T11:59:53.000Z","msg":"左手交右手"},{"pid":"9e373d0a61b1470c9245d4cc2d818e40b5b52aa2","tid":1042208,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-01T12:02:38.000Z","msg":"puma質地垃撚圾"},{"pid":"cc796c3dba039a260b9502e2b865eebd5c6e7869","tid":1042208,"uid":53498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"65c3c9dc23d8c5331af9ad17079d3983963b8b46","tid":1042208,"uid":53498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-01T11:56:43.000Z","msg":"唔撚貴合約,要一個月轉一次款"},"citedBy":0,"replyTim